import math

def factorial_fibonacci(n):
    fib_series = [0, 1]
    while fib_series[-1] <= n:
        fib_series.append(fib_series[-1] + fib_series[-2])
    fib_series = fib_series[:-1]
    return [math.factorial(i) for i in fib_series]
